      "description": "Hey there! You have to check out this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a scratch or a speck of dust anywhere! It drives like a dream and has been loved so much, but it's time for a new home. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one for you! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
