    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is delivered via the legendary S54 straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, mechanical engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. This example is in museum-grade condition; the subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the VANOS system has been overhauled to ensure peak variable valve timing performance. Zero deferred maintenance, original factory VIN stickers on all panels, and a chassis that remains as rigid as the day it left Regensburg. A true driver\u2019s specimen for the discerning collector.",
